name: gitspell - spellcheck for code
body:
### Welcome to Gitspell
Making the world a better place, one typo at a time.
```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ gitspell check
```
Or integrate gitspell into your repo.

### Want your repo git spelled, Contact me
[@bhaskerkode](http://twitter.com/@bhaskerkode) or [github.com/bosky101](http://github.com/bosky101)
